# Data Automation - Mahkamah Agung Scraper

## Overview

This project is a Python-based web automation and data extraction tool designed to automate the retrieval of public information from the Indonesian Supreme Court (Mahkamah Agung) website. The automation streamlines repetitive data collection processes, reduces manual effort, and improves efficiency when accessing and downloading court-related documents.

## Features

* Automated website navigation
* Automated search and data retrieval
* Automated document downloading
* File organization and storage
* Reduced manual data collection process
* Repeatable and scalable automation workflow

## Technologies Used

* Python
* Playwright
* SeleniumBase
* Web Automation
* Data Extraction

## Project Structure

```text
playwright-ma/
│
├── ma_scraper.py
├── sb_Mahkamah Agung.py
├── downloads/
├── downloaded_files/
└── README.md
```

## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Franlyjoshua/Data_Automation.git
cd Data_Automation
```

### Create Virtual Environment

```bash
python -m venv venv
```

### Activate Virtual Environment

Windows:

```bash
venv\Scripts\activate
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Usage

Run the automation script:

```bash
python ma_scraper.py
```

or

```bash
python "sb_Mahkamah Agung.py"
```

The automation will perform the configured workflow and store downloaded files in the designated folders.

